{"id":"d4c85ac24414e7ff54a3d3312421b735a7eb03f7b88b5683e0f3900c35b0c906","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:6"],["ref","GEN","1","6"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","0e3eb0f9e0b848fb1350a6e0e47b690512f2c4d7e563f6ce854bf33ca03eb544"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"And Elohiym said, “Let there be a firmament between the waters, to separate the waters from the waters.”","sig":"ac0e6988a0c80ad262d1b6041d4e32ab161a5176371e03cb33a950bc616371596160c6d19ce305c5ec5a47cd486a3c683df6e4998829247ec3b626ec30a48492"}
{"id":"01ce1a3eed2ae1b2f37a3ae0fe2a66d28f568b53b509069ebe796c218ef1d534","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:7"],["ref","GEN","1","7"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","4a3df9c5b45fc7a95e15c7b6c6afc8cfbc8790fdbc01815efee4c77b9e5d9861"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"So Elohiym made the firmament and separated the waters beneath it from the waters above. And it was so.","sig":"85bda5ebbf97567e6d30e06dfa16206c327302ea62300683619b69f9b89c464e4579c99166536e4d682d8fae3a97b1fbe8f57c4b843582b5dda7dc1dc0906bab"}
