{"id":"500051057483d04dd86dddd465fb1e8dbd69a4d5cbac61f96f9c586ab78bdf5b","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:25"],["ref","GEN","1","25"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","2044a67d10b5d745a3c286a18ef2b0ab3dd708d51f346a2458f6a00583bbc3fb"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Elohiym made the beasts of the earth according to their kinds, the livestock according to their kinds, and everything that crawls upon the earth according to its kind. And Elohiym saw that it was good.","sig":"20c4f395c35b853007677d56793ab82767b16aa3b3dfb0c89953b213880ef1d2245c36908af91f158e60173a022959a56fd9b491f77e5ad64efe4b8236b723a6"}
{"id":"caa8e8b01dde3e069fab8a55d7181166c4a98af26e25c1e2f191d63663f53845","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:26"],["ref","GEN","1","26"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","6353bee029694366e9523f79b8ce656974b31a8954ad1efc6f43adfd8dd52040"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Then Elohiym said, “Let Us make man in Our image, after Our likeness, to rule over the fish of the sea and the birds of the air, over the livestock, and over all the earth itself and every creature that crawls upon it.”","sig":"849b8ab8130167ea1ae93878c1adfd508438a9ae5c91cbfb1d2db9422c23b69254424c13bdaa257ebbcfb7e857bfb6b7c6e6b92669d10b66451b695db9efc9d9"}
{"id":"b31e1f3321f30aba4b44c59ec881f7bfd48634f7cbb080607dcb3bc47d7f6f02","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:27"],["ref","GEN","1","27"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","6b8586e785d8f5811a453a1f079bb5603f362ecc4175b3cbdd9c44f3bb5c336b"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"So Elohiym created man in His own image; in the image of Elohiym He created him; male and female He created them.","sig":"e4af53bfe33eab211f0e326d7f20c7a1ef3fe135e2438b0d2564a3945e0d59a5fcb490f5c6f30b3a0b65cbf752581587d8c51d10166cf779dbe25cfe1a882f1e"}
{"id":"250ec1285eb9cca4778d7867b75b3150a08f29100b2ae56f08b38b28a6fb86a0","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:28"],["ref","GEN","1","28"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","8a4911c2094db235c3c72efb8000908d4dde71031e62a357e65617caf5925e3b"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Elohiym blessed them and said to them, “Be fruitful and multiply, and fill the earth and subdue it; rule over the fish of the sea and the birds of the air and every creature that crawls upon the earth.”","sig":"fc7b1cb8fd73b1a0fad456be0505a9d23d64feeea70eb212cd053fb58f7f16196163586f374df7f28dc662d56c00b6989a24dc5f29aef8378416a51efc199a29"}
{"id":"e62d36b257fbd2a31bc8dfa079debf263b62831e547ca778eac90a3774594475","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:29"],["ref","GEN","1","29"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","5ff133b2b378ea34188d37bc57de46d590f9db6c9127004b347d0fa3c0e9f735"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Then Elohiym said, “Behold, I have given you every seed-bearing plant on the face of all the earth, and every tree whose fruit contains seed. They will be yours for food.","sig":"7fc1a2dfa7ae1410afe7387251ae5e51b86d3c67a0c08c59b3ff8329f2ae10f715183497ec09e34babd75e41d9ab60ff2416a9d842beba5fdb63a5dd77fb5f5e"}
{"id":"acf68277971c506743063b84ebf702ad94396bf5b79b85c939722f7d3fef1289","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:30"],["ref","GEN","1","30"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","d8262455b5ba3ed2899056ab225e71d2dc8db1e38a309923992fa6b2dcad076a"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"And to every beast of the earth and every bird of the air and every creature that crawls upon the earth—everything that has the breath of life in it—I have given every green plant for food.” And it was so.","sig":"1246840b28f60b945871f171bac29ef02af354de45b7075323fc2836a8f91bd4c47540256b7ce00dab9d9cce63442862ff15cde2fde2353de24cd626d3e5f52a"}
{"id":"77875aa983c77a035e31ee8fbadd058e6b9c2e20e3d56761141c1f3d2ad08c1e","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:GEN:1:31"],["ref","GEN","1","31"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","1264507f1bdb958da28d5cb2c51129dd95872969de53503aa6939053db510198"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"And Elohiym looked upon all that He had made, and indeed, it was very good. And there was evening, and there was morning—the sixth day.","sig":"55328eed78387fb897fa504bccbe16858076a3cf1541bf9d12c17d71b1e7c5e0e7b2fb328c44c36dc9277b580b62fbc7991bdf1a20332469846fd55d575e3339"}
{"id":"d8e6e9df6baacf48fdf36a9ff3e2e919d00ff716ab310f4b2d8f57de37deac41","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:1"],["ref","JHN","3","1"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","647ac2e446d3b3799503f4252b1664e6d3c7b5317daf2394489169809f9a6c9d"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Now there was a man of the Pharisees named Nicodemus, a leader of the Jews.","sig":"0c4b10edf98d7d0e2163f4a8944a663e35e42167c82ceab7cb1e9c3d9bf2b8af58662b2cacd78424bb1d130766da06668c77fdaa69d93978e112d2aa46150004"}
{"id":"e0576819da873254517176cf22f45bc48db4966a82a867be59954a5fe5f2f42e","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:2"],["ref","JHN","3","2"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","56971b8be7e9ef6b88d88eee144c59cfc8019615d15346f8a15e756b63ac8aec"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"He came to Yahusha at night and said, “Rabbi, we know that You are a teacher who has come from Elohiym. For no one could perform the signs You are doing if Elohiym were not with him.”","sig":"700c363e78c41eea3793172ce7e6111310dc5ab158809ea4e5d0ec3e56470f7bffa57966fa9925241a3828b6b110f5666d30be7f552c8fafd83067b678c386de"}
{"id":"941e64d4edf626b27a7a2c170571c9fa6977ed17d04eb170e512ecbca5f7f0d7","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:3"],["ref","JHN","3","3"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","813b5d9a94fabe4c7e40dc47f973a1c40f631d01e27b25cb3461f1b8121f5b0e"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Yahusha replied, “Truly, truly, I tell you, no one can see the kingdom of Elohiym unless he is born again.”","sig":"43f4b72e7ddf8fc856bc27e3736bdceae9b0d4b5e8fdc9d188246eb25f571f8bf6cbb8f74a176b7a6fbe234496abbb6c7be335642f3a1c9b037f9e05f4998654"}
{"id":"5af8cc7895e04c6210617b89823e928f00e92863eed309253cc675476fb65a9f","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:4"],["ref","JHN","3","4"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","9d95405f840afe471be810355493f3da679224d23d13b33827939904ade2d77c"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"“How can a man be born when he is old?” Nicodemus asked. “Can he enter his mother’s womb a second time to be born?”","sig":"49e0df3b942df3b3b804b80b44b74839217f78b2cf39883d81bd42e6ba1112e717e8c187b5ab334896e13c525c6af91727e0bb278b2fa923d2f879e8683a030d"}
{"id":"69bbfac2428f890f0d4e631b3814e9d1c351946a15954b77bf5d9a07df5e6660","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:5"],["ref","JHN","3","5"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","610983d8e3e084f6358b7b3ee121123391accef2262fa4dd70fb1e452ab735f7"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Yahusha answered, “Truly, truly, I tell you, no one can enter the kingdom of Elohiym unless he is born of water and the Spirit.","sig":"9900a1a6fb9a004e28e1c6de47e053e9723edeef6104b2efc0c911fa55abe467552a779d55de7058dd5c821c72e5ff9278af4578792688abca9c4dab0f1efe34"}
{"id":"4b778a1c4d4c283c61c8e9192868ce1b5b2d07fbd4f5185716f65850180b8c6c","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:6"],["ref","JHN","3","6"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","5ed308611a3c6ccf92ebb1bb1893c7a2141d64247bd6bdb5dd61d2b7ca4108a6"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Flesh is born of flesh, but spirit is born of the Spirit.","sig":"a110826800d28f76fcc94d160b7c059cb4eb311fd153a9b36988c187365c95173750c75cf20f5ac1c3e3d1797283d191e7d003088de4872ba4789c9d24a22b43"}
{"id":"032e08fe5ef8c1fe90b0268394a5ef8973dadae6941b64acc9633b6834fc6eaa","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:7"],["ref","JHN","3","7"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","c2c3e9f325471e88a2d9c61d7f8c3655aeb5b1ab9408990ad1be3238f2835617"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Do not be amazed that I said, ‘You must be born again.’","sig":"1e5ba6e11e806da2fa19174822f5dcbe18e33e600e3a7cb2ca504e5f6953bd4786330bbf4e4707467fe06f0aa41df4e797dcb66971f8575e6981d0137833de22"}
{"id":"239a493a79168069e056027fae0cb54b7012e373de4036450f82023908c9b4a0","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:8"],["ref","JHN","3","8"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","f3f6560b42e20c6c30b1d004a9f6482d83e84c04f5669ac3281f8aa88eb9319e"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"The wind blows where it wishes. You hear its sound, but you do not know where it comes from or where it is going. So it is with everyone born of the Spirit.”","sig":"4c0b3836b754d54d65d42fe4c15cbcc56bfc80860be2fb330b48c209abd47dd692c6bafd8594a81510f7fdde78200e50c38398e5a68e5696bf0302f2176cb42d"}
{"id":"fc5f1b0509bb556eec861fb922661037e70d45bb769a1c05e2b21176e4d9ef88","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:9"],["ref","JHN","3","9"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","c6dfd2dd40a2391b27f7aecf527f3acb63ab5d15c9189325a4dba58b3376991f"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"“How can this be?” Nicodemus asked.","sig":"3ee908eb9484f2a45094e4b842bf88cbbfadfc7c1378ed119967e09529b3a7fa51d5be51c57d1f393f0293c360491bbd0a6c2b1b93e84854d99582842786424b"}
{"id":"4416c86c76a3457da3097a943eca8087ef4f752d2018dfb78360b73c03dab8c0","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:10"],["ref","JHN","3","10"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","a6969c65416cd24a310c94ed7ed3d4aeaa0007c25c108de21b103bddc7fe0c0e"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"“You are Yashar'el’s teacher,” said Yahusha, “and you do not understand these things?","sig":"d8bd3e434dba67c59c77e38a293853878d3817c2ca05b4cd4c53284a39c1564dc0d40279271b91fbcf6c87802ef43c7ccb3e0425648bb4553ff91cdb292ce675"}
{"id":"2ac138c2e7f8fe21e97ff73dbaf33db6d4ddb87a76234b52a38637496627954e","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:11"],["ref","JHN","3","11"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","a43ea3c84ebc3086bbc4a7414311f09a8a7163b5921815706b5af895fa981796"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Truly, truly, I tell you, we speak of what we know, and we testify to what we have seen, and yet you people do not accept our testimony.","sig":"f6fadc87f6cd7a65e39ebfebb494bb6b9ce455d01344ba6970f5f8ef393ab4b261273141ee07b48173c794966f0055a5f6e35dae564ffca3bd56d5681a29ea32"}
{"id":"870b9ff67f43f2ecb073d7950c4a8e6da5239be1a6e1d31b9f7505113c139b80","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:12"],["ref","JHN","3","12"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","f05cf537dd8f82a41357d2952fc58a9df1f482713203ceda238f29054fb1f904"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"If I have told you about earthly things and you do not believe, how will you believe if I tell you about heavenly things?","sig":"94d4fd62af58cd3fa7ff08e8f7a4fc0728a431e8dc5b9f08b9f685ae893751363a836c9b3cae78312d1927b7a030fca4f5564a52aee85d9d4b6d52382e68201e"}
{"id":"1696d1af741d2ed5ba3927233f879c7ffd70722c29c28f45e631c0bb36e872ba","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:13"],["ref","JHN","3","13"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","458a96766c540de539e23decb805c8a7cf3814bdcc9844f83cac2e8f99f9d7ae"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"No one has ascended into heaven except the One who descended from heaven—the Son of Man.","sig":"28f4b6e7d96530fc96d2ba40af619c080841214e3615f93645dfc1e29a6f72ca1f7ea1ad313cb09f20e3ccf03fcf420d6dc5155bb9a022ec81510b3eebdf8a46"}
{"id":"fddd891f90aeabb69dc5933fe18015c074fdf71ad9e8302b3ad2240ff28438ee","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:14"],["ref","JHN","3","14"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","3735903e5d5ad3d7a542728668ec53f70df6e5bae7ff0c30ccad148c4ffea26a"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Just as Mosheh lifted up the snake in the wilderness, so the Son of Man must be lifted up,","sig":"1aabda33de47a1318b38a2c9c3c8f476194fb5e599991aa67a85050ebfff1597c1e5b8e439e8813f8edc0b7a939ca3199cc0dae5fff40621ac3f543b353da1fe"}
{"id":"52e0fcf8bea29a0553b91364245faacdabebe40a2e0d5fe0a9a550de7c556ad4","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:15"],["ref","JHN","3","15"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","e4f21ce456aa236f6f970b083babcb22f80dd0458c12502a39deed969caccc20"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"that everyone who believes in Him may have eternal life.","sig":"d9c7d93ee4acaa63c9bd365b5bb55766fdbc7afeb05cf2a1bac609d4406c9343f77ca96171545880a454debd3afbec35505a613035143c2e4487fd59e6370c39"}
{"id":"4c442ed597ba54f0ce9fd44a043c89525535b7975865f5e84e2dffbc7c0a1b2e","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:16"],["ref","JHN","3","16"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","1a6b807f04c69192f8c250cbe3af82e85b329971a569be7fd9aab1e6e380c303"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"For Elohiym so loved the world that He gave His one and only Son, that everyone who believes in Him shall not perish but have eternal life.","sig":"0cfe695ec82a3c5aebb3bc12abd310eea91421eb1601da5940970396fbc5a883a2c0e19b3b6d3c37a444f98999ba511875dc884aaaebbef894567bab266cdcaa"}
{"id":"1aa82de97f02c83656fe10ad4a8f0b4390337254df0513ea69f49295a5faa3d3","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:17"],["ref","JHN","3","17"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","0a8f15dfff0380c23597fd0bdba1c6049174e06c93723c48d0d75a7b39ee0cd6"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"For Elohiym did not send His Son into the world to condemn the world, but to save the world through Him.","sig":"517f0a754358a5b2f60efdc86e90d65887831be7da5d6a3eb36d3011657e8395b9635aee830f1a4a9406871a3cefa757527cb4194e1f42324df64a71ca383b50"}
{"id":"ced1ebd6e92998271452e463b4098c8318c86bd693b501b41342cf9f92f030c2","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:18"],["ref","JHN","3","18"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","4c73108c0355d9b8d399b317a4a01784c79c0a008c0b3dde4ef352003ba4d73e"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Whoever believes in Him is not condemned, but whoever does not believe has already been condemned, because he has not believed in the name of Elohiym’s one and only Son.","sig":"dd7dfef94c4aefe1866fa278e88bc661d8129fd21ce5ad3a1d596c5cc2d1234e119cff774a397298eaedee59fb01cc1e01f9e741cc63f5052fa68f8b7a8acee3"}
{"id":"41cb22b3c7e0e201357d8c070d2b768f8847deb0177c42b1376c19dd3279873b","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:19"],["ref","JHN","3","19"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","f93860a2d5bf0ef55b8b1726c5f43d10ff611e222d2191e8a18f436ec8fcb161"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"And this is the verdict: The Light has come into the world, but men loved the darkness rather than the Light because their deeds were evil.","sig":"bfa2750d16fa8ab11c333a892fc3c97ffdb2ec8365e94aadaa4189107f22c5d2834a42f38e42bb8ec4ce5a434fe654ee1a3397dfe3f79cb6924ddc30ec693225"}
{"id":"c075c3068fd2b5646d6dff050ec4e39b97f85b71121e6cb32ef2784e8b39ae35","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:20"],["ref","JHN","3","20"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","477363ed8f01e1c4c67e602c41abf3deb4519ee648e7993076db8e34aa624f69"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Everyone who does evil hates the Light, and does not come into the Light for fear that his deeds will be exposed.","sig":"13084f8703ada60cea9d03c7e69a5e79063e3e91a71a29ef1bc9b245775b2a57b7501d7671ae3845cfea4e859ba59131413bd43bbbdee325fe8784c54e0a200f"}
{"id":"2353ecf82b770644170181b0b58c4b4f778b8a196f5edddcebfc2cd59d1e882e","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:21"],["ref","JHN","3","21"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","a3a034597e2267f8538726df4ee0f35a274adb5e9d99a0fadc5ddd525ff6da50"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"But whoever practices the truth comes into the Light, so that it may be seen clearly that what he has done has been accomplished in Elohiym.”","sig":"3e88e46eb561a9c1ff711270ea82e8f81f0c0366ed3e99f363d3d24a64208e71282d0ea9cc00c824889ca9fe82ea2890cfab5a155f45028b5d367859a3db95f9"}
{"id":"196ed2b7251db26debf4880a4d7d089be493d9a2172918eb0aa8fe7ba4c2ec31","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:22"],["ref","JHN","3","22"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","015c79974a20bf7429833ea25dfa84bba02673416924a70a2db689faae742232"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"After this, Yahusha and His disciples went into the Judean countryside, where He spent some time with them and baptized.","sig":"fa086b9f7da6b8d0f7b3a4c20e8db4cda98d1581b39dcf4e505dda1d724fe0daabc948cf6fac4bc0bba7131686eb1db21ec3503144c50591c4eb17d344bba5d8"}
{"id":"35c444a09272e1f95307937dd2dacc22df7abfb6e34bb97db040967bbf2eab42","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:23"],["ref","JHN","3","23"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","ed4e0deb159527c65c1794036441c75ef5027e24d87a4047ce23feccd78e9294"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Now Yahuchanon was also baptizing at Aenon near Salim, because the water was plentiful there, and people kept coming to be baptized.","sig":"88713326a529ee6f71a9ea5ed1f98fa2bb5eaba6c8940a8e0368fedb5d0f68bf4970cb8c3a63539863fba042865f4db6a6138d41efd1aeca2835a2730fed19bc"}
{"id":"51fed9990caa05a9f4711fb6b309e98a727ff53c0b6846c9d558cedd96f34f5f","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:24"],["ref","JHN","3","24"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","fe718a3650b92abdfd5a9b9de51ae76cdd1fd4d3ca03a97663f227ccab0ae335"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"(For Yahuchanon had not yet been thrown into prison.)","sig":"a75daa2fa9159375a88bc792696f5199220340b2ee5a169d2d80dae5d30c6591e65c134b1b573dd184b2921496a9c2f30816eaea7fea0e43d7999753204113bf"}
{"id":"fdcabda21b3940c62d76cbef8bbf728746e6506f256981bb00a54ecd6eb685fa","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:25"],["ref","JHN","3","25"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","d49bd2797d017cea83cfad7acc81c036171808bb73ba31b46cfae3fa93fa93b3"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Then a dispute arose between Yahuchanon’s disciples and a certain Jew over the issue of ceremonial washing.","sig":"b351d2acac05daa50a00dfc16961fde09e88865799271fff2f24ec0a09cfe0841aa7dcdfcc0ca49de8c31a865d5cd2d061ba5226e53a57a48b312f38047aa085"}
{"id":"86cb2a9c44fb935d7862d558621b3b000d9963dcefd74123246c0705f5802ca7","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:26"],["ref","JHN","3","26"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","7d266e2d3ad8d52b519b97182649832d9a8879265111d27539e9729bf2cc0e15"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"So Yahuchanon’s disciples came to him and said, “Look, Rabbi, the One who was with you beyond the Yarden, the One you testified about—He is baptizing, and everyone is going to Him.”","sig":"2d0a1e85c77b1aa62e25a7ba47331f26c85e6b1470193b70d8881f8b68a4a221c9cc30c5c631348f9d28e377ad0ca291e43cf5bf940459e9633ae709b1a53409"}
{"id":"f41b37bd6f74292979c3d2b884146f273967fbccc34065307c0d84847652eda5","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:27"],["ref","JHN","3","27"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","d3ab1727bc77fe1f1d7edb8a522db661ae0ebc94ddf8458efe773701cd8b6214"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Yahuchanon replied, “A man can receive only what is given him from heaven.","sig":"12ab115f822d7517a7b4c8ce91b4526f3f8712e19e4c62ace9b9e547074f3348f5318021cba88f41af57a0c9bd659f0b39a33dfa389def5ddf01038feda0f8d4"}
{"id":"3e913c29304ed43fa909286c4c01bf4c61f7b818956b22197175731589221d3f","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:28"],["ref","JHN","3","28"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","e6a6b8c62a74a3449f5fe3e3abbd706193d2fbf6eca649b733c04a8f12d0bafd"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"You yourselves can testify that I said, ‘I am not the Mashiach, but am sent ahead of Him.’","sig":"81c218f90a4ab98592fc3d058c644e41296cb80d19bc01846842075685e96eb1ce63592d1a875808e12ac0d002fed79c53c8f1957a5311086b056b8a548c53fd"}
{"id":"299bc348e7418b7ddb2156c69d7e99d69da6717dc481187b0983517543a70347","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:29"],["ref","JHN","3","29"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","88c1ecb3c51be0e739d1db2212e21b0f67e77e4d61c20f69fca95fc068c395ce"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"The bride belongs to the bridegroom. The friend of the bridegroom stands and listens for him, and is overjoyed to hear the bridegroom’s voice. That joy is mine, and it is now complete.","sig":"4c2c5ce30b6fbb086feea0fc498b35c35086573910f10f65a44d1327ee4c5a206eec4a14476055b2d55e22ff6064538921740c4c8450d42a1091ca7712d9862d"}
{"id":"2ac423b28bfc4b27611a0146f644b1064165a3df1ebf00719e2256ff20ce1866","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:30"],["ref","JHN","3","30"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","cc61821956d1c5d4e2d63e6c26a79e08b0f54d8f70a9704daf35a192543b6a3b"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"He must increase; I must decrease.","sig":"a8d739e1c1448171e74c02654b1e9b1a28faa1c4f9e5e562acbff8410affe688b498c2a7620d28e1398d23fff397edf3a2abebafd67b0fe98f79938135554c32"}
{"id":"46e0c11bd614de3e2cd1d3061721d9bf9b080d5272caed27c074c17f88dadaed","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:31"],["ref","JHN","3","31"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","a04dc5a78b43ddbc7a05ef909da3bec56446a3cd60648485253bc4191554ecc7"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"The One who comes from above is above all. The one who is from the earth belongs to the earth and speaks as one from the earth. The One who comes from heaven is above all.","sig":"3ccda396200c84759a472742ff119cdf4c690db458326dfbf976c4e822ba528e8727ed29186767d8c090213d22a4eb4804fe2e0edb6137eb31e492acb4c892d9"}
{"id":"fb305217f3a2b7ac5bb0995e6ae44ebfd02a9989e9c1402ab34136a9225a2ccc","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:32"],["ref","JHN","3","32"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","0677d7402e0247b61a3a05e43d9924e3f31cef0f1d13de5a17ac6244c9834520"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"He testifies to what He has seen and heard, yet no one accepts His testimony.","sig":"8a37d892a54a80ff3361bd951ec89b5afb00ca289677117423bc4db5c7f827881e94ac14c0a31622eb58788c6f08bd0456d4a00b713e1dd4db00e25e354394ca"}
{"id":"19e2e8179398ee4ef8af38677a0d4aa2aaa1f4c35907d324df02d5c62b25fe3c","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:33"],["ref","JHN","3","33"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","f8957cc58ff784dd2925b668be173c997393619103bb4780053c037aa4a236ff"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Whoever accepts His testimony has certified that Elohiym is truthful.","sig":"b406ff4578efda9448e4ba9bdeacec30d43aef226de7730e978cd1fce2c79ea766b4ebd2c5d2326136da819a36eec0fc8cdec826bd1a05fc464313a8c7e8cd04"}
{"id":"36b9c53b74b6ddb383c843fb98b2a9129b213f29948ad5eaf48367f825597d03","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:34"],["ref","JHN","3","34"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","104a894d62ff5707697a0a9437be0a60f4f48b82911c73987b22694a4de10700"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"For the One whom Elohiym has sent speaks the words of Elohiym, for Elohiym gives the Spirit without limit.","sig":"c1f9bf9a97b8d31308afc7e899015300e4a842d0954462d68a18cf95d6a447964f4914c39410a2d510879e4a2421b1a983818609fbcea1b8826c3b43cd4a3484"}
{"id":"bfcbf1132fc3b4e2dd2d841052941c30ace5627db3eb6eb1aacff96c38f1d29c","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:35"],["ref","JHN","3","35"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","5ff3223dafcc9230a12528052fb76412d0e627ca9a16c697d5b32c9d9b6eddf2"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"The Father loves the Son and has placed all things in His hands.","sig":"a185e799df8a4f223c4119a3c1bbfa33af298a838dc1a06d5913fe73f4e6500a4bf3b1491439f6343be5705fda43f96e09753409234bc2b0bf0a67daf99a426c"}
{"id":"8d933d985cf92c0cd6f357b65f32cd39bb11c8227d91fee1795c5c7dbea97b3f","pubkey":"d5e6b8d1134eb2c23cf876cbc306a09e41a16ccf22d9535672c57c1ed3a8809b","created_at":1781481600,"kind":30700,"tags":[["d","neoos-en-2026:JHN:3:36"],["ref","JHN","3","36"],["t","translation:neoos-en-2026"],["lang","eng"],["h","c04f993275619f582437503a7c371e788a7aa502f0a8f319b9c2eb9f03dad555"],["src","BSB"]],"content":"Whoever believes in the Son has eternal life. Whoever rejects the Son will not see life. Instead, the wrath of Elohiym remains on him.”","sig":"9e59fe8b5f97d3f176dfb7946649267a8f0d35bc675db9b94e1c58473f532a64a600f68239d233e338c8041161f7dad67c5d44af094fcaebf56f05139ea26c11"}
